org.apache.spark.sql.types

Interface DataTypeParser

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    DDLParser

    public interface DataTypeParser
    This is a data type parser that can be used to parse string representations of data types provided in SQL queries. This parser is mixed in with DDLParser and SqlParser.
